        },
        {
          "title": "Services Provided",
          "body": "The Tamam app provides a platform connecting car wash owners with customers. Services include: order management, biker tracking, branch and staff management, and payment records. The company is not responsible for any disputes arising between service providers and customers."
        },
        {
          "title": "Privacy & Data Protection",
          "body": "We are committed to protecting your personal data in accordance with Saudi Arabia's Personal Data Protection regulations. Your data is stored securely and will not be shared with any third party without your consent, except as required by law."
        },
        {
          "title": "Payments & Invoices",
          "body": "All amounts shown are in Saudi Riyals and include VAT. The company may adjust subscription prices with at least 30 days advance notice. Fees paid for expired periods are non-refundable."
        },
        {
          "title": "Service Provider Obligations",
          "body": "The service provider is committed to delivering agreed services at high quality, adhering to specified working hours, not sharing customer data with any other party, and immediately reporting any issue affecting service delivery."
        },
        {
          "title": "Service Termination",
          "body": "Either party may terminate the agreement with 14 days advance notice. The company reserves the right to immediately suspend an account in case of violation of any of these terms or proven fraudulent practices."
        },
        {
          "title": "Governing Law",
          "body": "These terms and conditions are governed by the laws of Saudi Arabia. Saudi courts have jurisdiction over any dispute arising from the application of these terms, with competent courts located in Riyadh."
        }
      ]
    },
